Installation

Clone repository:

git clone <repository-url>

Create environment:

python -m venv .venv

Activate:

Windows:

.venv\Scripts\activate

Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt
Running the Dashboard

From project root:

streamlit run app/streamlit.py
Example Results

The framework produces:

Historical VaR 95%:
1.58%

Parametric VaR 95%:
1.76%

Monte Carlo VaR 95%:
1.77%

Expected Shortfall:
2.68%

Values depend on the selected portfolio and historical data.

